<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She regularly puts on a sultry display on social media as an Ann Summers brand ambassador.</p>

<p>And Chloe Ross opted for a casual look as she enjoyed a day out with a group of friends at Sketch in Mayfair over the weekend.</p>

<p>The former TOWIE star, 27, appeared in good spirits after enjoying cocktails with her pals and departed the venue in a black sheer top with a knot around her waist that displayed her taut abdomen.</p>

<p>Looking good: Chloe Ross, 27, opted for a casual look as she enjoyed a day out with a group of friends at Sketch in Mayfair over the weekend</p>

<p>The garment featured a collar and a lined detail while Chloe also sported a pair of blue jeans for the outing.</p>

<p>The TV star wore a pair of black flats and carried a matching handbag while she added to her outfit with gold hoop earrings.</p>

<p>Chloe completed her look for the outing by styling her brunette locks into a ponytail.  </p>

<p>Chloe's former castmates have been filming the new series of ITVBe's The Only Way Is Essex, which celebrates the show's 10-year anniversary in recent weeks. </p>

<p>Outfit: The former TOWIE star wore a black sheer top with a knot around her waist that displayed her taut abdomen</p>

<p>Style: The garment featured a collar and a lined detail while Chloe also sported a pair of blue jeans for the outing</p>

<p>Fun: Chloe appeared in good spirits after enjoying cocktails with her pals</p>

<p>The 10th anniversary series was due to start filming in March 2020, but ITV bosses made the tough decision to put the production on pause due to the coronavirus pandemic.</p>

<p>Fans were left without their Essex fix until the show came back with a vengeance on Sunday night, with former cast member Amy Childs returning.</p>

<p>There will also be surprise appearances from some of the show's other big stars from the past decade.  </p>

<p>Paul Mortimer, Head of Digital Channels and Acquisitions for ITV, added: 'After 10 years, TOWIE is still going strong and remains the number one show on ITVBe.</p>

<p>'We're thrilled to be welcoming back new and old faces for the upcoming mega-series as the show celebrates this special anniversary.'</p>

